# Примеры баг-репортов

## Bug-001: Кнопка Login неактивна в темной теме

**Status:** Open
**Priority:** High
**Severity:** Major
**Environment:** Safari 26.1, MacOs Tahoe 26.1 (25B78)

**Description:**
При переключении на темную тему и вводе корректных данных кнопка Login остается неактивной.

**Steps to Reproduce:**
1. Open https://opensource-demo.orangehrmlive.com/
2. Switch to dark mode (if available)
3. Enter "Admin" in Username field
4. Enter "admin123" in Password field
5. Observe Login button state

**Expected Result:**
Login button becomes active and clickable

**Actual Result:**
Login button remains disabled

**Attachments:**
- Console logs show: `button[disabled] CSS property override issue`
- Screenshot available in Jira attachment

**Reproduction Rate:** 100% (5/5 attempts)

---

## Bug-002: Session timeout не показывает уведомление

**Status:** Fixed
**Priority:** Medium  
**Severity:** Minor
**Environment:** All browsers

**Description:**
При истечении сессии пользователь автоматически разлогинивается без предупреждения.

**Steps:**
1. Login with valid credentials
2. Wait 15 minutes (session timeout)
3. Try to navigate to any page

**Expected:**
Modal popup "Your session will expire in 5 minutes" appears

**Actual:**
User is silently logged out, redirected to login page
